  "title": "Internal Audit Executive (Oversea Travel Required) #NKC",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Assist in internal audits of regional group entities and progressively lead smaller audits</p></li><li><p>Support audit planning by establishing risk hypotheses and performing data analysis</p></li><li><p>Draft clear and factual audit observations with practical recommendations</p></li><li><p>Conduct audit follow-ups and present findings to senior management</p></li><li><p>Provide consultation and support on internal controls and SOX compliance as required<br /></p><p><strong>\nWill need to travel extensively across the Southeast/West Asia & Oceania regions (1-2 weeks per month)</strong><br /><strong></strong><br /><br />Interested applicants may email resume to kellychooi@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Chooi Kelly (CEI Registration No: R25136207)</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (EA: 99C4599)</p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted</p><p></p></li></ul>",
